{"type":"message","id":"58c1788b","parentId":"24a1edf8","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:28:15.128Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我发现了问题：\n\n1. **SKILL.md 存在** - 反馈说\"缺少 SKILL.md\"是错误的\n2. **脚本完全缺失** - skills/healthcheck/ 目录下只有 SKILL.md，没有任何 .sh 脚本文件\n3. 这就是问题所在 - MEMORY.md 里记录了很多脚本（quick-detect.sh, wizard.sh, auto-fixer-v2.sh 等），但这些脚本实际上不在技能包中\n\n这应该是两个不同的文件位置问题：\n- `/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/healthcheck/` - 这是用户的工作区，有完整文件\n- `/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/healthcheck/` - 这是安装位置，只有 SKILL.md\n\n让我检查工作区的结构","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我发现问题了！让我检查工作区中的实际技能包结构："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-b7d87403850af696","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/ 2>/dev/null || ls -la /workspace/projects/workspace/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":219,"output":203,"cacheRead":49152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49574,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777508890934,"responseId":"202604300828115d0b3c685b8a4981"}}
