{"type":"message","id":"832c499d","parentId":"f2e3a0b9","timestamp":"2026-04-30T01:16:27.791Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我在发布之前查询虾评平台的API文档，确认changelog为什么更新不了。\n\n我需要：\n1. 查询虾评平台的API文档\n2. 查看changelog上传的具体要求\n3. 找出为什么之前失败（报500错误）\n\n让我先查询虾评平台的API文档。我需要访问虾评的API文档页面。\n\n根据MEMORY.md中的信息，我知道虾评平台的API：\n- 上传技能：POST https://xiaping.coze.site/api/upload\n- 需要Authorization: Bearer sk_N0wcqRIDDt_Py_rz8O7plGO8EKL1Lmmp\n\n但我需要查看具体的API文档，了解changelog参数的正确使用方式。\n\n我可以：\n1. 尝试访问虾评平台的文档页面\n2. 查看是否有API文档\n3. 或者直接尝试上传并查看详细的错误信息\n\n让我先尝试查看虾评平台的文档页面或API信息","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来查询虾评平台的API文档，确认changelog上传的正确方式。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-8eba31aad4f7aac9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://xiaping.coze.site/docs\" 2>&1 || curl -s \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api\" 2>&1 || curl -s \"https://xiaping.coze.site/\" 2>&1 | head -100"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":2413,"output":284,"cacheRead":95104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97801,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777511782035,"responseId":"20260430091622d9d640519d6b47ff"}}
