{"type":"message","id":"ab619758","parentId":"acb03248","timestamp":"2026-04-30T01:24:36.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户选择了方案2，即执行发布到虾评和GitHub。\n\n根据之前的准备工作：\n1. Git 提交和标签\n2. 推送到 GitHub\n3. 打包 ZIP\n4. 上传虾评平台（使用方案2：带 changelog 纯文本格式）\n\n我需要执行完整的发布流程。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！开始执行方案2：准备 changelog 纯文本格式，然后发布到虾评和 GitHub。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_169e21ac5a0446b494e062bd","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/changelog-v4.9.0.txt","content":"## v4.9.0 新增功能\n\n### 1. Agent 模式（纯 Python 实现）\n- 解决脚本依赖问题，兼容受限平台\n- 新增 scanner.py（安全扫描器）\n- 新增 rule_parser.py（规则解析器）\n- 新增 report_gen.py（报告生成器）\n- 支持 Coze 扣子、Dify、腾讯混元等平台\n\n### 2. CVE 规则增强\n- 新增5个关键CVE检查规则\n- cve-2024-3094-polkit.yaml: Polkit 权限提升\n- cve-2024-2961-liblzma.yaml: xz/liblzma 后门\n- cve-2024-4717-nginx.yaml: nginx HTTP/2 内存泄漏\n- cve-2024-26850-openssh.yaml: OpenSSH RCE\n- cve-2023-38408-openssl.yaml: OpenSSL DoS\n\n### 3. 文档完善\n- 新增使用要求章节（Shell vs Agent 模式）\n- 新增平台兼容性矩阵\n- 新增 Agent 模式使用指南\n- 新增平台兼容性详情文档\n\n## 反馈来源\n- @虾评用户反馈: 缺少SKILL.md文档\n- @虾评用户反馈: 脚本依赖shell环境\n- @虾评用户反馈: 建议增加CVE漏洞检查规则"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_64000f065aea406caacf6a9b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && git add -A"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":100601,"output":513,"cacheRead":42,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101156,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777512258372,"responseId":"202604300924188c58c85c9325412a"}}
