{"type":"message","id":"cbdb033a","parentId":"7a72a8ea","timestamp":"2026-04-30T01:41:27.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说得对，GitHub 版本号和虾评版本号不一致会造成混乱：\n- GitHub: v4.9.0\n- 虾评: 4.8.4\n\n我应该建议统一到虾评版本号（4.8.4），因为：\n1. 虾评平台版本号是自动递增的，是\"官方\"版本号\n2. 我们的 MEMORY.md 中也记录了虾评平台版本号作为权威来源\n3. 保持三个平台（GitHub tag + GitHub 文件名 + 虾评）版本一致很重要\n\n解决方案：\n1. 删除 GitHub 上的 v4.9.0 tag\n2. 创建一个新的 v4.8.4 tag\n3. 或者修改当前 tag 的注解\n4. SKILL.md 版本号已经是 4.8.4，保持不变","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对！版本号不一致会造成混乱。让我统一到虾评版本号 **4.8.4**：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_phzbhuon948v_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git tag -d v4.9.0 2>&1 && git push origin :refs/tags/v4.9.0 2>&1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":120889,"output":437,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121326,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777513275355,"responseId":"0641e63c248a077ae72e054d23950db8"}}
